<Layout title="Delete Account">
  <h1>Request Account Deletion</h1>
  <p>If you signed up using Facebook Login and want to delete your data from our systems, please follow these steps:</p>

  <ol>
    <li>Send an email to <a href="mailto:you@example.com">you@example.com</a></li>
    <li>Use the subject line: <strong>Delete My Account</strong></li>
    <li>Include your full name and the email used to log in</li>
  </ol>

  <p>We will process your request within 7 days and confirm once completed.</p>
</Layout>
